column3: targeted professional improvement activities are provided for teachers and professional staff based on student performance data and\ridentified student needs.\r\r2017-18:\r•All teachers participate in District-wide Academies that focus on professional development in New California State Standards implementation\ras well as English Learner support\r•ILT team participate in 4 all day sessions to plan and review our professional development cycle\r•Teacher teams participate in weekly collaboration sessions throughout the year to analyze student work
column4: participate in professional\rdevelopment and plan for instruction\r•All teachers continue to receive training on Reading Comprehension and writing strategies led by Dr. Bonnie McGrath and on-site Resource\rTeacher\r•All teachers continue to receive training making thinking visible in Math given by District Math Resource Teacher\r•All teachers participate in peer observations to give and receive feedback on professional learning\r•All teachers receive training on GLAD strategies to support English Learners\r•All teachers receive ongoing training on technology for classroom instruction
